---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../../components/CTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Continuous Annealing Line Accessories For High Throughput" description="You operate high-speed processing lines where downtime impacts output. Our accessories for continuous annealing lines are built for speed and durability.">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-4">Furnace Application Solutions</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 mb-8 leading-tight">Continuous Annealing Line Accessories For High Throughput</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 mb-12">
        <p>You operate high-speed processing lines where every second of downtime impacts your total factory output. Our accessories for continuous annealing lines are built for speed, durability, and extreme thermal stability across long production runs. You will ensure that your steel or aluminum products reach the exact mechanical properties required by your customers by using our reliable temperature probes and atmosphere control components.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Technical Challenge</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Continuous lines face extreme tension and high-velocity gas flow. You need precise temperature feedback for each segment of the line.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Weigu Solution</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Weigu provides ultra-stable thermocouples and atmosphere monitoring systems. You maintain perfect metallurgical properties across the entire strip length.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="bg-blue-900 text-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Key Components For This Application</h2>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> High-Speed Sensors</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Flow Control Valves</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Radiant Tube Fixings</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> High-Temp Seals</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="mt-16">
        <CTA title="Optimize Your Annealing Line Today" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
